l census 2011</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.un.org.np/maps/district-maps/western/Kailali.pdf UN map of the municipalities of Kailali District]\n*[http://www.ddckailali.gov.np Official website of ddc Kaialali]\n*[https://www.citypopulation.de/php/nepal-mun-admin.php?adm2id=7105 City Population - Gauriganga Municipality in Nepal]\n{{Kailali District}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Kailali District]]\n[[Category:Municipalities in Sudurpashchim Pradesh]]\n\n{{Sudurpashchim-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n<!--See the table at Infobox settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  -->\n|name                   = Gauriganga Municipality\n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = \u0917\u094c\u0930\u0940\u0917\u0902\u0917\u093e\u093e \u0928\u0917\u0930\u092a\u093e\u0932\u093f\u0915\u093e\n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        = [[Municipality]]\n|motto                  = <!-- images and maps  -->\n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|image_flag             = \n|image_seal             = \n|image_map              = \n|photo1a                = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|pushpin_map            = Nepal Sudurpashchim Pradesh#Nepal\n|pushpin_label_position = bottom\n|pushpin_mapsize        = 300\n|pushpin_map_caption    = Location in Nepal\n<!-- Location -->\n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = {{flag|Nepal}}\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Provinces of Nepal| Province]]\n|subdivision_name1      = [[Sudurpashchim Pradesh]]\n|subdivision_type2      = [[Districts of Nepal|District]]\n|subdivision_name2      = [[Kailali District]]\n|subdivision_type3      = [[Administrative divisions of Nepal#Cities and Municipality of Nepal|Municipality]]\n|subdivision_name3      = [[Gauriganga Municipality]]\n|subdivision_type4      = [[Ward]]\n|subdivision_name4      = [[11]]\n|local